{"tid":311594,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打可以寫下埃及神祇既故?_?","createTime":"2017-07-06T17:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T05:47:43.000Z","uid":17065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51e120a203f41ae47b6a93eab24339673157ba07","tid":311594,"uid":17065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前有睇過果套 埃及守護神既書<br />\n覺得個作者寫得好好 好有想像力<br />\n但佢係寫左後人 唔係寫以前既故事<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好多空間可以寫咁<br />\n唔知有冇巴打會想寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個作者係故事都有提及 以前有法老王會借助神既力量<br />\n但無點詳細講 ,而佢個神話個開始 拉 , 芭絲堤果D神都無點描寫<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打有書可以推介既話都OK架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c20002f6e22d6093e427d3153cabe8002d9da6","tid":311594,"uid":87495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:07:33.000Z","msg":"反而想問下巴打你睇套守護神係咩書名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好有興趣"},{"pid":"7b309623ee76ba35381ae15d006d9d6d447a5d7e","tid":311594,"uid":17065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而想問下巴打你睇套守護神係咩書名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好有興趣</blockquote><br />\n好似就係叫 埃及守護神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd4b39ac493f5d41d0b298db49ea9bc45c6e6c9","tid":311594,"uid":38615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"我個故寫晒全世界既神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1437bdf2673527a59a6c5fafdcc9b714412cc78","tid":311594,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ebc60bb7